    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basics without spending a fortune. It\u2019s got the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect from an older used car, but there\u2019s still plenty of value here for the right buyer. If you\u2019re practical, handy, or just want cheap transportation with potential, this one is well worth a look.",
